appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Enhancing the Real Table Experience

New Features:
* Max Odds – Now adjustable in settings.
* Come Bet Behavior – Automatically comes down after a 7 is rolled.
* Auto Bet Control – New setting to automatically turn bets ON/OFF on the Come Out Roll.

Bug Fixes:
* Rebet Fix – No longer clears ATS or Fire Bets.

Keep the feedback coming! Feel free to email me with any suggestions or features you’d like to see in the app.
